snippet.textDisplay: I couldn’t watch this when it first came out because it took me back to losing my dog Sparky a year ago. He was only 7 years old and was happy and healthy till the week of his passing. I didn’t have very many friends during this period so losing my best friend was and still is hard. I still talk about him to others as if he is still here because I’m so proud and grateful for who he was. Sparky also as you mentioned in your video had an emotional intelligence, it’s like you are one with your dog. It’s a bond like no other. I’m truly sorry for your loss. Since I’ve lost Sparky, in my time of need I pray for god to send me Sparky to be with me in spirit. Cookie is still with you every step of the way supporting you.
